Best Buy Co Inc said its sales forMarch rose to 26.1 mln dlrs from 11.9 mln dlrs in thecomparable 1986 period.    It said sales for the fiscal year ended March 31 rose to329.5 mln dlrs from 113.1 mln dlrs a year earlier.    The company said sales performance was based on theaddition of 12 new retail facilities. Reuter&#3;